  "detailed_description": "<strong><i>GunQuest is an action-packed RPG, where you use firearms to combat fantasy creatures. Craft guns, explore an open world, team up with allies, and conquer the infinite plain in GunQuest!</i></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Interact with the Developer</h2><i>Also, Psst...</i> <strong>GunQuest has a discord server!</strong> Follow the development process and give input on the direction of the game!<br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay Features</h2></strong><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Overworld Caravan Travel!</li><li>Fast paced combat!</li><li>Enemy Variety!</li><li>Interesting NPCs!</li><li>Dynamic Dialogue Options!</li></ul></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944700/extras/17c7ef9feb8843b8fd5862d0cb6a43f5.avif?t=1717416997\" width=384 height=384 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features In Production</strong></h2><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>NPCs travel in tandem with the caravan!</li><li>New playable characters!</li><li>Native Tribe Weapons!</li><li>Extended Map Size!</li><li>Bullet Type Variety!</li><li>Rune/Magic System for Guns!</li><li>Crafting System!</li><li>Caravan Upgrade System!</li></ul></i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find New Weapons!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944700/extras/88278304effbb8c370e26fc3defd063c.poster.avif?t=1717416997\" width=246 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944700/extras/88278304effbb8c370e26fc3defd063c.webm?t=1717416997\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight Enemies!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944700/e